R19-1-103.
Change in Proprietary Interest No licensee shall transfer, assign or make any change in ownership in such business, directly or indirectly, nor shall a partner purchase or otherwise acquire the interest held by any other controlling person or partner in the business, without notifying the Director within 30 days and filing such application, questionnaire or other documentation required by this Title.
