R19-1-209.
Broken Package Prohibited -- Off-sale Premises No off-sale retailer shall have upon his licensed premises any broken package of spirituous liquor, as defined by A.R.S. Ã¯Â¿Â½ 4-101.
This rule applies to the actual container and not to the shipping case.
