R19-1-218.
Change of Address When a street number or other official designation of address of the licensed premises is changed, the licensee shall notify the Department on a form prescribed by the Director within 15 days of such change.
The license shall be surrendered upon the issuance of a replacement license which reflects the current address of the licensed premises.
