R19-1-228.
Advertising, Misleading No licensee shall label for sale any spirituous liquor which is dispensed through equipment that would directly or indirectly lead the public to believe they are purchasing a brand, grade, or class of spirituous liquor, including beer and wine, which is actually not being sold or used.
