R19-1-252.
Interim Permit/Tax Violations The Director may refuse to issue an interim permit or issue a license until arrangements have been made with the taxing authority to satisfy the payment of all delinquent taxes.
Any arrangements must be verified in writing from the applicable taxing authority and submitted to the Director.
