ARTICLE 3.
UNLICENSED PREMISES DEFINITIONS AND LICENSING TIME-FRAMES Editor 's Note: The following Section was amended under an exemption from the Arizona Administrative Procedure Act (A.R.S.
Title 41, Chapter 6) pursuant to Laws 1996, Ch. 307 Ã¯Â¿Â½ 18.
